View.Name: CustomerSubTotal
View.ViewDetails: <![CDATA[SELECT dbo.Invoice.InvoiceDate, dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID, dbo.Invoice.CustomerAc, dbo.Invoice.AddressBill, dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid, dbo.Invoice.EndPayment, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal - dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid AS Overdue FROM dbo.Invoice INNER JOIN dbo.SumInvoiceDetails ON dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID = dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.InvoiceID ]]>

View.Name: History
View.ViewDetails:
<![CDATA[SELECT dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID, dbo.Invoice.CustomerAc, dbo.Invoice.AddressBill, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal, dbo.Invoice.EndPayment, dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal - dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid AS Overdue FROM dbo.Invoice INNER JOIN dbo.SumInvoiceDetails ON dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID = dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.InvoiceID
]]>

View.Name: MainSumTotalCash
View.ViewDetails: <![CDATA[SELECT dbo.CashInvoice.InvoiceDate, dbo.CashInvoice.InvoiceID, dbo.CashInvoice.AddressBill, dbo.CashInvoice.TotalPaid, dbo.SumCashTotal.SumTotal, dbo.SumCashTotal.SumTotal - dbo.CashInvoice.TotalPaid AS Overdue FROM dbo.CashInvoice INNER JOIN dbo.SumCashTotal ON dbo.CashInvoice.InvoiceID = dbo.SumCashTotal.InvoiceID ]]>

View.Name: SumCashTotal
View.ViewDetails: <![CDATA[SELECT InvoiceID, SUM(Total) AS SumTotal FROM dbo.CashInvoiceDetailes GROUP BY InvoiceID ]]>

View.Name: SumInvoiceDetails
View.ViewDetails: <![CDATA[SELECT InvoiceDetails.InvoiceID, Sum(InvoiceDetails.Total) AS SumOfTotal FROM InvoiceDetails GROUP BY InvoiceDetails.InvoiceID;]]>

View.Name: SumListPaid
View.ViewDetails:
<![CDATA[SELECT dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID, dbo.Invoice.CustomerAc, dbo.Invoice.AddressBill, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal, dbo.Invoice.EndPayment, dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid, dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.SumOfTotal - dbo.Invoice.TotalPaid AS Overdue FROM dbo.Invoice INNER JOIN dbo.SumInvoiceDetails ON dbo.Invoice.InvoiceID = dbo.SumInvoiceDetails.InvoiceID WHERE (dbo.Invoice.EndPayment = N'Yes')
]]>

View.Name: SunAllTotals
View.ViewDetails: <![CDATA[SELECT CustomerAc, SUM(SumOfTotal) AS SumOfSumOfTotal, SUM(TotalPaid) AS SumOfTotalPaid, SUM(Overdue) AS SumOfOverdue FROM dbo.History GROUP BY CustomerAc ]]>

View.Name: View_CustomerPaiment
View.ViewDetails:
<![CDATA[SELECT     CustPaimentID, InvoiceID, CustomerAc, TotalOfGoods, AmountPaid, TotalOfGoods - AmountPaid AS Overdue
FROM         dbo.CustPaiment
]]>
